How to cite. The usage of Optimus should be accompanied with the following
    citation:
    Nicholas Andre G. Johnson and Aleksandr B. Sahakyan, "General purpose
    adaptive optimisation engine in R", in preparation, 2018.

Contributing to Optimus. We are interested in continuously adding additional
    functionalities and optimisation modes to Optimus. You are encouraged to
    contribute code or issues to this repository for further incorporation into
    the package. For details on how to do this, please see the package
    web-site: http://optimus.atgcdynamics.org.
